== Installation ==

Two libraries must be linked to this project:

- FFTW : http://www.fftw.org/
- Boost(ublas) : http://www.boost.org/

FFTW is Fast Fourier Transform (FFT) library. In this project, the library is used for fast convolution in a distance compensation context.

Boost is used for its UBLAS subset, a set of objects dedicated to linear Algerbra.



